<A>__{shining below the dome (which we now see as a series of dome like structures standing off without end) a marvelous crystalline city of great openness, building clusters, green plazas, fountains... multi leveled but human scale, crisscrossed by the flickering clear tubes of the maze cars. closer angle rooftops as a maze car slides softly to a stop. rooftop the runner the hatch opens and a man in a hurry leaves the maze car and runs swiftly along the rooftop and disappears into an open elevator which instantly starts to descend.}
